There were no other sightings in Chaska on or around November 17th 2010
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on my way to Glencoe from Chaska with my mom and I looked out my window to the SW and saw one bright light being followed by 4 other lights flying in a strange formation. I've seen many aircraft in my life and seen many flying formations but this was most unusual they were flying close to each other and around and away, I lost sight of the objects as they flew NE
